data.description: Well kept, upgraded home in desirable Northwest neighborhood. 4 Bed/2.5 Bath split bedroom floor plan. 24'' tile and laminate wood flooring throughout. 3 car garage has epoxy flooring. Single car garage has a mini split system, pre-wired for cable and insulated for casita. This home site is on the 2nd largest lot in the neighborhood. Two large side yards with 5 hole putting/chipping green, brick patios and wrap-around artificial turf in the backyard. Must see to appreciate all this home has to offer. Open and bright floor plan. Washer, dryer, wine fridge in kitchen and refrigerator in the garage do not convey.
